<number box="[526,585,1761,1785]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" value="1940.0">1940</number>
; p. 
<number box="[636,709,1761,1785]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" value="43.0" valueMax="44.0" valueMin="42.0">42–44</number>
, figs. 
<number box="[787,858,1761,1785]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" value="29.5" valueMax="30.0" valueMin="29.0">29–30</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) was found on leaves of 
<taxonomicName box="[1172,1281,1761,1785]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Viola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="biflora">
<emphasis box="[1172,1281,1761,1785]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">V. biflora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Liro" box="[1300,1436,1761,1785]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" refString="Liro, J. I. (1940) Neue Eriophyiden aus Finnland. Annales Zoologici Societatis Zoologicae - Botanicae Fennicae, Venamo, 8 (1), 1 - 67." type="journal article" year="1940">
Liro (
<number box="[1369,1427,1761,1785]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" value="1940.0">1940</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
observed a prodorsal shield that was slightly extended over the gnathosoma (
<emphasis box="[1011,1344,1797,1821]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">Vorderrand etwas vorgezogen</emphasis>
), with a reticulate pattern and an opisthosoma with 
<number box="[643,713,1833,1857]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" value="37.0" valueMax="38.0" valueMin="36.0">36‒38</number>
dorsal semiannuli somewhat larger and smoother and about 
<number box="[1408,1436,1833,1857]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" value="50.0">50</number>
ventral semiannuli. This mite is a junior homonym of the above species that needs a new name (
<taxonomicName authority="Amrine" authorityName="Amrine" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Cecidophyes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="finlandia">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">Cecidophyes finlandia</emphasis>
Amrine
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis box="[329,431,1905,1929]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">in litteris</emphasis>
). Unfortunately, these species have not been described again after 
<bibRefCitation author="Liro" box="[1179,1311,1905,1929]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" refString="Liro, J. I. (1940) Neue Eriophyiden aus Finnland. Annales Zoologici Societatis Zoologicae - Botanicae Fennicae, Venamo, 8 (1), 1 - 67." type="journal article" year="1940">
Liro (
<number box="[1242,1303,1905,1929]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" value="1940.0">1940</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1436,1185,2037]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">
<collectingCountry box="[197,228,1942,1966]" name="American Samoa" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">As</collectingCountry>
far as is known, two further unnamed and undescribed species under the genera 
<taxonomicName box="[1132,1207,1941,1965]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1132,1207,1941,1965]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">Aceria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1261,1374,1941,1965]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Eriophyes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1261,1374,1941,1965]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">Eriophyes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were recorded respectively on 
<taxonomicName box="[435,517,1978,2001]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Sinapis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="10" pageNumber="57" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
